07\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:659:\"<p>Do you want to track your blog authors with Google Analytics? When you&#8217;ve multiple authors writing content on your blog, you&#8217;ll need to track them individually to find out the best performers and vice versa. In this article, we&#8217;ll show you how to set up author tracking in WordPress with Google Analytics. Install MonsterInisghts for [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/author-tracking-wordpress-google-analytics/\">How to Set Up Author Tracking in WordPress with Google Analytics</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11519:\"<p>Do you want to track your blog authors with Google Analytics? When you&#8217;ve multiple authors writing content on your blog, you&#8217;ll need to track them individually to find out the best performers and vice versa.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll show you how to set up author tracking in WordPress with Google Analytics.</p>\n<h3>Install MonsterInisghts for Author Tracking in Google Analytics</h3>\n<p>By default, there&#8217;re no settings in Google Analytics to track your blog authors. You&#8217;ll need to add custom settings for enabling author tracking.</p>\n<p>Using the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/pricing\" target=\"_blank\">MonsterInsights plugin</a> is the easiest way to enable author tracking on your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress site</a>. MonsterInsights is the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-analytics-solutions-compared/\">best Google Analytics plugin for WordPress</a>. </p>\n<p>Once you enabled the tracking, you&#8217;ll get amazing reports about the pageviews, bounce rate, and the most popular author of your blog. You can also add other custom dimensions to track the authors in WordPress.</p>\n<h3>Setting Up Author Tracking in WordPress with Google Analytics</h3>\n<p>The first thing you need to do is to install and activate the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/pricing\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MonsterInsights\">MonsterInsights Pro</a> plugin. For more details, see our step-by-step guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"How to Install a WordPress Plugin\">how to install a plugin in WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>Upon activation, go to <strong>Insights &raquo; Addons</strong> to install and activate the <strong>Dimensions</strong> addon.</p>\n<p>Now, you&#8217;ll need to connect Google Analytics with your WordPress blog.</p>\n<p>Simply go to your MonsterInsights account and copy the license key. Next, go to <strong>Insights &raquo; Settings</strong> in your WordPress blog.</p>\n<p>In the <strong>License Key</strong> field, paste the key and click on the <strong>Verify Key</strong> button.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/licensekey.jpg\" alt=\"License Key\" width=\"775\" height=\"330\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222893\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/licensekey.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/licensekey-300x128.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/licensekey-768x327.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Once verified, click the <strong>Tracking</strong> tab from the top section. From there, you&#8217;ll need to visit <strong>Custom Dimensions</strong> in the left-hand menu.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/customdimensions.jpg\" alt=\"Custom Dimensions- author tracking\" width=\"775\" height=\"452\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222894\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/customdimensions.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/customdimensions-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/customdimensions-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>On this page, click on the <strong>Add new custom dimensions</strong> link and it&#8217;ll display a dropdown. In this dropdown, you&#8217;ll need to select <strong>Author</strong> as your custom dimension.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/selectauthor.jpg\" alt=\"Select Author- author tracking\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222895\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/selectauthor.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/selectauthor-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/selectauthor-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Click on the <strong>Save Changes</strong> button to store these settings.</p>\n<p>Next, log into your Google Analytics account and open your blog link to add custom dimensions for author tracking.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/googleanalyticsproperty.jpg\" alt=\"Your website in Google Analytics account\" width=\"420\" height=\"239\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222286\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/googleanalyticsproperty.jpg 420w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/googleanalyticsproperty-300x171.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px\" /></p>\n<p>Once opened, you&#8217;ll need to go to the <strong>Admin</strong> tab from the left menu. Under the Custom Definitions column, you&#8217;ll need to click on Custom Dimensions.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/click-custom-dimensions.jpg\" alt=\"Click on custom dimensions- author tracking\" width=\"560\" height=\"258\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222896\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/click-custom-dimensions.jpg 560w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/click-custom-dimensions-300x138.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, click on the <strong>New Custom Dimension</strong> button in the table.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/new-custom-dimension.png\" alt=\"New custom dimension- set up author tracking\" width=\"446\" height=\"92\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222897\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/new-custom-dimension.png 446w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/new-custom-dimension-300x62.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 446px) 100vw, 446px\" /></p>\n<p>It&#8217;ll open the form to create a new custom dimension. In the Name field, you&#8217;ll need to add <strong>Author</strong> and click on the <strong>Create</strong> button. Keep all the other settings as-is.</p>\n<p>Last, you&#8217;ll need to match the index number of Google Analytics with <strong>Custom Dimension ID</strong> that&#8217;s available in your WordPress MonsterInsights settings.</p>\n<p>You can see the index number for Author under the <strong>Index</strong> column in Google Analytics. Simply note this index number.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/author-tracking.jpg\" alt=\"Author tracking\" width=\"560\" height=\"88\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222899\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/author-tracking.jpg 560w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/author-tracking-300x47.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, visit the <strong>Insights &raquo; Settings</strong> page in your WordPress admin area. Under the <strong>Tracking</strong> tab, you&#8217;ll need to go to Custom Dimensions from the left-hand menu.</p>\n<p>If the Custom Dimension ID is same as the index number in Google Analytics, then you don&#8217;t need to do anything. If the ID is different, then make sure to enter the same number you noted from Google Analytics&#8217; index column for the Author dimension and click on the &#8216;Save Changes&#8217; button.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/customdimensionsid.jpg\" alt=\"Custom Dimensions ID\" width=\"775\" height=\"193\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222900\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/customdimensionsid.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/customdimensionsid-300x75.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/customdimensionsid-768x191.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, you&#8217;ll need to add a custom report in your Google Analytics account to track the blog authors properly. In Google Analytics, you&#8217;ll need to go to <strong>Customization &raquo; Custom Reports</strong> from the left menu. Look for the <strong>Report Content</strong> fields and define the metric groups.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll need to add <strong>Author</strong> in the Dimension Drilldowns and click on the <strong>Save</strong> button.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/custom-reports-in-customization.jpg\" alt=\"Custom reports\" width=\"620\" height=\"381\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222901\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/custom-reports-in-customization.jpg 620w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/custom-reports-in-customization-300x184.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>It&#8217;ll display the traffic report for your Author dimension. You can monitor the page views and bounce rates according to the blog authors.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/author-report.jpg\" alt=\"Author report\" width=\"620\" height=\"449\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222902\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/author-report.jpg 620w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/author-report-300x217.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>To view further custom author reports, select <strong>Author</strong> as a secondary dimension in Google Analytics.</p>\n<p>First, you&#8217;ll need to visit <strong>Behavior &raquo; Site Content &raquo; All Pages</strong>. From here choose any primary dimension (for example: Page Title) and go to the <strong>Secondary Dimension</strong> dropdown below it.</p>\n<p>Under the Custom Dimensions, click on the <strong>Author</strong> option to view the custom reports with other primary dimensions.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Google-Analytics-secondary-dimension.jpg\" alt=\"Secondary dimension\" width=\"295\" height=\"339\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222903\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Google-Analytics-secondary-dimension.jpg 295w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Google-Analytics-secondary-dimension-261x300.jpg 261w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 295px) 100vw, 295px\" /></p>\n<p>It&#8217;ll add the new author column and display author name next to each blog title. That way you can view more personalized reports for authors.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/author-report-1.jpg\" alt=\"Custom author report\" width=\"620\" height=\"388\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222904\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/author-report-1.jpg 620w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/author-report-1-300x188.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>In Google Analytics, you have various options to change the settings and view custom reports as needed. Google Analytics also allows you to export your reports as spreadsheets.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you learn how to set up author tracking in WordPress with Google Analytics.</p>\n<p>If you liked this article, you might also enjoy our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/set-download-tracking-wordpress-google-analytics/\" title=\"How to Set Up Download Tracking in WordPress With Google Analytics\">how to set up download tracking in WordPress with Google Analytics</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/author-tracking-wordpress-google-analytics/\">How to Set Up Author Tracking in WordPress with Google Analytics</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://www.isitwp.com/author-tracking-wordpress-google-analytics/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"Meta Slider Review [Tested]: Features, Usage and More\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/meta-slider/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/meta-slider/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 05 Oct 2018 10:57:40 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?post_type=isitwp_plugin&p=1954\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:545:\"<p>Meta Slider is a popular and highly rated free plugin that allows you to create image sliders. It has a few different options for slider styles and transition effects for your slides. In our Meta Slider review, we’ll take a look at its main features and user interface.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/meta-slider/\">Meta Slider Review [Tested]: Features, Usage and More</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18282:\"<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/metaslider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meta Slider</a> is a very popular, highly-rated plugin that allows you to create image sliders. It has multiple different options for slider styles and transition effects for your slides. In our Meta Slider review, we’ll take a look at its main features and user interface to test how great (or not) it really is.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/metaslider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1955\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-wordpress-plugin-review.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider WordPress Plugin Review\" width=\"961\" height=\"306\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-wordpress-plugin-review.png 961w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-wordpress-plugin-review-300x96.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-wordpress-plugin-review-768x245.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 961px) 100vw, 961px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>About Meta Slider</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/metaslider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meta Slider</a> is a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-slider-plugins-comparison/\">WordPress slider plugin</a> with both free and premium versions. Using Meta Slider, you can create basic image sliders and use them on your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress site</a> with shortcodes and <a title=\"What is a template tag in WordPress?\" href=\"http://www.wpbeginner.com/glossary/template-tag/\" target=\"_blank\">template tags</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/metaslider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meta Slider</a> was developed by Matcha Labs, a digital agency and product company based in the UK that specializes in WordPress and iOS development.</p>\n<h3>How to Set Up Your First Slider</h3>\n<p>After installing and activating the plugin, click on the new <b>Meta Slider</b> menu item on your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n<p>Then, click on the plus sign to get started.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1956\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-add-new.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - add new slider\" width=\"471\" height=\"514\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-add-new.png 471w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-add-new-275x300.png 275w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 471px) 100vw, 471px\" /></p>\n<p>You can click on the tab to edit the name of your slider.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1957\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-edit-name.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - edit slider name\" width=\"173\" height=\"61\" /></p>\n<p>Then, click the <b>Add Slide</b> button to add your first slide.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1958\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-add-slide-button.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - add slide button\" width=\"937\" height=\"133\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-add-slide-button.png 937w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-add-slide-button-300x43.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-add-slide-button-768x109.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 937px) 100vw, 937px\" /></p>\n<p>This works like the default WordPress <b>Add Media</b> button in your posts and pages. You can choose an image from your media library, or upload a new one. Then, click <b>Add to slider</b>.</p>\n<p>You can edit the description and add a link URL, if desired.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1959\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-edit-slide.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - edit slide\" width=\"940\" height=\"296\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-edit-slide.png 940w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-edit-slide-300x94.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-edit-slide-768x242.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" /></p>\n<p>Click on the <b>SEO</b> tab to change the title and add alt text. (The title does not display on your slider.)</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1960\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-slide-seo-tab.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - seo tab\" width=\"485\" height=\"234\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-slide-seo-tab.png 485w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-slide-seo-tab-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 485px) 100vw, 485px\" /></p>\n<p>Under the <b>Crop</b> tab, you can select some options for cropping the slide.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1961\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-crop.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - crop tab\" width=\"340\" height=\"287\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-crop.png 340w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-crop-300x253.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 340px) 100vw, 340px\" /></p>\n<p>On the right side of the page, you can choose the type of slider you want to create.</p>\n<p>The documentation doesn’t provide any details or examples of the different types except for this brief list:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Flex Slider</strong>: responsive, 2 transition effects, carousel mode</li>\n<li><strong>Responsive Slider</strong>: responsive and lightweight</li>\n<li><strong>Nivo Slider</strong>: responsive, 16 transition effects, 4 themes</li>\n<li><strong>Coin Slider</strong>: NOT responsive, 4 transition effects</li>\n</ul>\n<p>So, to find out what they look like, you&#8217;ll have to experiment and try each one.</p>\n<p>For the Flex Slider, only 2 transition effects are allowed to be selected.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1962\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-flex-options.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - flex slider options\" width=\"317\" height=\"525\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-flex-options.png 317w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-flex-options-181x300.png 181w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 317px) 100vw, 317px\" /></p>\n<p>Here’s what the Flex Slider looks like:</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1963\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-flex.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - flex slider\" width=\"711\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-flex.png 711w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-flex-300x148.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 711px) 100vw, 711px\" /></p>\n<p>The Responsive Slider only allows the Fade transition effect.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1964\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-responsive-options.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - responsive slider options\" width=\"309\" height=\"417\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-responsive-options.png 309w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-responsive-options-222x300.png 222w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 309px) 100vw, 309px\" /></p>\n<p>Here’s what Responsive Slider looks like:</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1965\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-responsive.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - responsive slider\" width=\"709\" height=\"347\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-responsive.png 709w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-responsive-300x147.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 100vw, 709px\" /></p>\n<p>For the Nivo Slider, you can choose from more transition effects (but still not all of them).</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1966\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-nivo-transition.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - nivo transition effects\" width=\"310\" height=\"514\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-nivo-transition.png 310w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-nivo-transition-181x300.png 181w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 310px) 100vw, 310px\" /></p>\n<p>There are also 4 different themes to choose from.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1967\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-nivo-themes.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - nivo slider themes\" width=\"312\" height=\"420\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-nivo-themes.png 312w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-nivo-themes-223x300.png 223w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 312px) 100vw, 312px\" /></p>\n<p>Here’s what the default theme looks like:</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1968\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-nivo-default.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - nivo default theme\" width=\"711\" height=\"352\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-nivo-default.png 711w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-nivo-default-300x149.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 711px) 100vw, 711px\" /></p>\n<p>And the dark theme:</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1969\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-nivo-dark.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - nivo dark theme\" width=\"1007\" height=\"552\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-nivo-dark.png 1007w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-nivo-dark-300x164.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-nivo-dark-768x421.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1007px) 100vw, 1007px\" /></p>\n<p>The Coin slider features just 4 transition effects.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1970\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-coin-transitions.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - coin transitions\" width=\"314\" height=\"523\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-coin-transitions.png 314w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-coin-transitions-180x300.png 180w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 314px) 100vw, 314px\" /></p>\n<p>Unlike the other themes, the Coin slider has no arrows. You must navigate by clicking the buttons at the bottom, so be careful not to select the “Hidden” option for navigation.</p>\n<p>The Coin slider seems to tile your images if they&#8217;re smaller than the slider size (the other types stretch them to fit):</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1972 size-full\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-coin-random-e1475614386541.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - coin random\" width=\"1028\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-coin-random-e1475614386541.png 1028w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-coin-random-e1475614386541-300x161.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-coin-random-e1475614386541-768x411.png 768w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-coin-random-e1475614386541-1024x548.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1028px) 100vw, 1028px\" /></p>\n<p>Under the <b>Advanced Options</b> area, you can customize your slider a bit more.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1971\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-advanced-options.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - advanced options\" width=\"313\" height=\"660\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-advanced-options.png 313w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-advanced-options-142x300.png 142w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 313px) 100vw, 313px\" /></p>\n<p>Once you’ve finished creating your slider, click the <b>Save</b> button.</p>\n<p>Under the <b>Usage</b> area on the right, you can copy the shortcode to display your slider, or click on <b>Template Include</b> to get the code to include it in your theme files.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1973\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-review-usage.png\" alt=\"Meta Slider Review - usage\" width=\"311\" height=\"202\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-review-usage.png 311w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/meta-slider-review-usage-300x195.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 311px) 100vw, 311px\" /></p>\n<h3>Get More Options With Meta Slider Pro</h3>\n<p>There’s a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/metaslider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">premium version of Meta Slider</a> that unlocks more options.</p>\n<p>It includes additional features like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Animated Layer Slides</li>\n<li>YouTube and Vimeo Slides</li>\n<li>Post Feed Slides: displays your latest posts or custom post types</li>\n<li>Theme Editor: customize the look of your slider using 30+ settings</li>\n<li>Thumbnail Navigation: displays thumbnails at the bottom of the slider for navigation</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Documentation and Support</h3>\n<p>The documentation provides a very basic overview of what this plugin can do, but it doesn’t provide much detail. It would be more useful if they had more examples and screenshots, as well as explanations of the 4 slider types, so users aren’t left guessing.</p>\n<p>If you buy the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/metaslider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pro version</a>, you&#8217;ll get access to priority support via a private ticket system.</p>\n<p>Users of the free theme can post in the forums at WordPress.org, but it looks like it can take a few weeks to get a response.</p>\n<h3>Pricing for Meta Slider Pro</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/metaslider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meta Slider</a> is a premium plugin that gives you a choice to start with its free version. You can install the free version first, try out its features to get familiar, and purchase its premium version only if it has what you’re looking for. </p>\n<p>The free version is available at WordPress.org for download and use. For a small business or startup, the free version can be enough. But the sliders will look very basic and commonplace. </p>\n<p>If you want to create unique and impressive sliders, you should purchase <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/metaslider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meta Slider Pro</a>. </p>\n<p>The premium version is for advanced users who want to make their sliders stand out from the crowd with maximum customization options. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/metaslider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meta Slider</a> has 5 pricing plans for its premium version. You can choose a plan depending on the number of sites you want to use Meta Slider on. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/meta-slider-pricing.jpg\" alt=\"meta-slider-pricing\" width=\"775\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222945\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/meta-slider-pricing.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/meta-slider-pricing-300x194.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/meta-slider-pricing-768x496.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/metaslider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meta Slider Pro</a> for <strong>1-2 site license</strong> costs $39, <strong>5 site license</strong> costs $79, <strong>20 site license</strong> costs $119, <strong>100 site license</strong> costs $189, and <strong>unlimited site license</strong> costs $289. Meta Slider Pro gives you a plenty of options to choose from, so you can buy a plan precisely according to your need.</p>\n<p>All the premium plans come with 1 year of automatic updates and 1 year premium support. The free version users can get only basic forum support at WordPress.org. </p>\n<p>You can try its premium version risk-free, as they have 30-day money back guarantee</p>\n<h3>Our Verdict on Using Meta Slider</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/metaslider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meta Slider</a> is a simple slider plugin that is easier to use than incredibly complex slider plugins like <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/revolution-slider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Slider Revolution</a> or <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/layerslider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LayerSlider</a>.</p>\n<p>However, the user interface isn’t as well-designed as it could be. Instead of matching the WordPress interface seamlessly, the system is a little jarring and takes some getting used to.</p>\n<p>It’s also unclear why there are 4 different types of sliders that&#8217;re so similar in design, with each very limited in features. Why can you only use the Fade effect on Responsive sliders? Why are the Coin sliders not responsive? It would make more sense to be able to select the styles and options you want individually, instead of having these 4 arbitrary names.</p>\n<p>The lack of information or previews for each slider type is frustrating as well, since you have to use trial and error to see what each one looks like.</p>\n<p>We would recommend using the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/soliloquy/\" target=\"_blank\">Soliloquy slider plugin</a> instead, since the interface seamlessly matches WordPress and it’s much easier to use. You can read more in our full <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/soliloquy/\">Soliloquy review</a>.</p>\n<p>We give <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/metaslider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meta Slider</a> 3 out of 5 stars. Here&#8217;s the breakdown of our review scores:</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/meta-slider/\">Meta Slider Review [Tested]: Features, Usage and More</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/meta-slider/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"10 Best WordPress Testimonial Plugins to Add Social Proof\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-testimonial-plugins/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-testimonial-plugins/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 04 Oct 2018 09:09:22 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"review plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"social proof\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"testimonial plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=222733\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:613:\"<p>Looking for the best WordPress testimonial plugins? Good idea! You do fantastic work, and your customers are happy. So why not share their feedback publicly on your website for all to see? Since there are so many WordPress testimonial plugins available, we know it can be difficult to decide which one to choose. To help [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-testimonial-plugins/\">10 Best WordPress Testimonial Plugins to Add Social Proof</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15472:\"<p>Looking for the best WordPress testimonial plugins? Good idea! You do fantastic work, and your customers are happy. So why not share their feedback publicly on your website for all to see?</p>\n<p>Since there are so many WordPress testimonial plugins available, we know it can be difficult to decide which one to choose. To help you out, in this article, we’ve narrowed your decision down to the 11 best WordPress testimonial plugins.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">1. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms.png\" alt=\"WPForms\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218485\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Renowned for being the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\">best contact form plugin</a> available for WordPress, WPForms can also be utilized as a top-notch testimonial plugin.</p>\n<p>With the Post Submissions addon, you can create an easy-to-use form for your clients to submit a testimonial to you, directly from your website. You can include features like a rating scale, because who doesn’t love getting gold stars for their work!</p>\n<p>After submission, the user’s testimonial will land in your WordPress dashboard area for you to review it before deciding whether or not to publish it.</p>\n<p>WPForms’ primary focus is on ease-of-use, making it an effortless process for both the client submitting the testimonial and you, the site owner, once you’re ready to publish their feedback.</p>\n<p>Read our <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/wpforms/\">full review of WPForms</a> for more information.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Started with WPForms Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/thrive-ovation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Thrive Ovation</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/thrive-ovation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ThriveOvation.png\" alt=\"Thrive Ovation\" width=\"775\" height=\"303\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222736\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ThriveOvation.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ThriveOvation-300x117.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ThriveOvation-768x300.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As one of the best WordPress testimonial plugins, Thrive Ovation is truly stunning. It helps you gather testimonials in 3 unique ways:</p>\n<p>First, it allows you to magically transform any WordPress comment left on your website into a ready-to-feature testimonial with just a single click of your mouse. No more copy / pasting necessary! It will even include the name and avatar of the user who left the comment.</p>\n<p>Second, Thrive Ovation integrates with Twitter and Facebook so that you can easily nab comments made about you, or your business, and import them into the plugin’s patented testimonial Rolodex. Unappealing screenshots are a thing of the past with this feature as Thrive Ovation not only imports the positive mentions, it also transforms them into aesthetically-pleasing, official-looking, testimonials.</p>\n<p>Third, this plugin allows you to fully automate the testimonial gathering process by letting you create dedicated testimonial submission pages, posts, and forms. You can even send automated messages to customers asking them for feedback, with a link to your testimonial gathering page. Truly, Thrive Ovation is one of the best WordPress testimonial plugins available.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/thrive-ovation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Thrive Ovation Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/testimonials-showcase/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Testimonials Showcase</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/testimonials-showcase/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialsShowcase.png\" alt=\"Testimonials Showcase\" width=\"775\" height=\"375\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222737\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialsShowcase.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialsShowcase-300x145.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialsShowcase-768x372.png 768w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialsShowcase-330x160.png 330w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Testimonials Showcase allows you to beautifully display customer feedback in a grid or a slider.</p>\n<p>It has an easy-to-use front-end submission form, so clients can submit their testimonials directly on your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress website</a>.</p>\n<p>In addition, Testimonials Showcase is translation ready. You’ll never have to worry about language barriers preventing clients from talking about, or potential customers from reading about, how awesome you are ever again.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/testimonials-showcase/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Testimonials Showcase Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/testimonials-slider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Testimonials Slider</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/testimonials-slider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialsSlider.png\" alt=\"Testimonials Slider\" width=\"775\" height=\"363\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222738\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialsSlider.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialsSlider-300x141.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialsSlider-768x360.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Gutenberg Editor supported and GDPR compliant, Testimonials Slider stays ahead of the curve by being consistently updated with needed improvements to keep you ahead of the game.</p>\n<p>Customize your testimonials slider with gorgeous built-in templates, and then feature it on your site using a shortcode or widget. Absolutely zero coding skills required!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/testimonials-slider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Testimonials Slider Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonials-widget/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Testimonials Widget</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonials-widget/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialsWidget.png\" alt=\"Testimonials Widget\" width=\"775\" height=\"256\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222740\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialsWidget.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialsWidget-300x99.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialsWidget-768x254.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The ease of a widget combines with the eye-catching beauty of an image slider with the Testimonials Widget plugin.</p>\n<p>Slide, carousel, and fade transitions are all available options. You can also filter your slideshow content by WordPress’ tags, categories, or post IDs. Best of all: Testimonials Widget’s mixed content capabilities allow you to feature text, images, and videos all in one slideshow. You can display any type of testimonial content any way you desire!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonials-widget/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Testimonials Widget Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonial-rotator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Testimonial Rotator</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonial-rotator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialRotator.png\" alt=\"Testimonial Rotator\" width=\"775\" height=\"246\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222741\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialRotator.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialRotator-300x95.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialRotator-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Utilizing the ability to create a custom post type, Testimonial Rotator gives you an incredibly simple way to manage testimonials on your WordPress Website.</p>\n<p>Testimonial gathering is simplified and even includes a star rating system. And displaying the testimonials? Even simpler, thanks to shortcode and widget options.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonial-rotator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Testimonial Rotator Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-testimonials/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Easy Testimonials</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-testimonials/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/EasyTestimonials.png\" alt=\"Easy Testimonials\" width=\"775\" height=\"245\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222742\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/EasyTestimonials.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/EasyTestimonials-300x95.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/EasyTestimonials-768x243.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As the name implies, Easy Testimonials boils down to one adjective: easy.</p>\n<p>Whether you want to embed your testimonials in a page or post, or add them to your sidebar as a widget, you absolutely can. And zero coding skills are required thanks to the handy-dandy shortcode feature.</p>\n<p>Easy Testimonials supports images, so adding a face to an author’s name is simpler than ever. It also uses the latest technology to make your testimonials appear in your website’s search results.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-testimonials/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Easy Testimonials Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonial-add/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Testimonial Slider</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonial-add/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialSliderFree.png\" alt=\"Testimonial Slider\" width=\"775\" height=\"326\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222743\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialSliderFree.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialSliderFree-300x126.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialSliderFree-768x323.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Unlimited testimonials sliders are at your fingertips with the Testimonial Slider plugin.</p>\n<p>Highly customizable, Testimonial Slider features custom colors, a variety of layouts, and multiple transitions to assist you in creating the most elegant showcase possible for your client feedback.</p>\n<p>Don’t like sliders? You can also use their list format feature.</p>\n<p>Best of all, Testimonial Slider offers front-end and backend submission forms to make the testimonials gathering process hassle-free. Everything can be controlled with ease from your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonial-add/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Testimonial Slider Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonial-basics/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Testimonial Basics</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonial-basics/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialBasics.png\" alt=\"Testimonial Basics\" width=\"775\" height=\"257\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222745\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialBasics.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialBasics-300x99.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TestimonialBasics-768x255.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Testimonial Basics proves that “basic” doesn’t mean “bad.” Nor does it mean that it’s not a full-featured plugin!</p>\n<p>Going above and beyond “the basics,” Testimonial Basics offers up 6 widget display options and 4 page displays, each with customizable colors, backgrounds, and fonts.</p>\n<p>Translation-ready, RTL compatible, and GDPR compliant, Testimonials Basics includes easy-to-use input forms for testimonials gathering. It also includes one of our favorite features: star ratings!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonial-basics/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Testimonials Basics Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/strong-testimonials/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. Strong Testimonials</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/strong-testimonials/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/StrongTestimonials.png\" alt=\"Strong Testimonials\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222746\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/StrongTestimonials.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/StrongTestimonials-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/StrongTestimonials-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Developer-friendly, Strong Testimonials is beefy and well-stocked with features. From its front-end form for testimonial gathering, to its beautiful sliders for display options, Strong Testimonials is definitely one of the best WordPress testimonial plugins.</p>\n<p>If you use Polylang, WPML, or WPGlobus on your website, you’ll be pleased to know that Strong Testimonials integrates with each of those plugins, making it fully translation-ready. You can also jazz up your displays with YouTube, Twitter, Instagram, or Facebook embeds.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/strong-testimonials/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Strong Testimonials Today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you discover the absolute best WordPress testimonial plugins.</p>\n<p>If you enjoyed this article, you might also like our post on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/custom-user-registration-form-wordpress/\">how to create a custom user registration form</a> in WordPress.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-testimonial-plugins/\">10 Best WordPress Testimonial Plugins to Add Social Proof</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-testimonial-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"NextGEN Gallery Review: Is It the Best Gallery Plugin?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/nextgen-gallery/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/nextgen-gallery/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 03 Oct 2018 08:12:27 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?post_type=isitwp_plugin&p=879\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:535:\"<p>Looking for the best image gallery plugin for WordPress? NextGEN Gallery is one of the oldest and most popular image gallery plugins in the WordPress.org directory, but is it the best? Read our NextGEN Gallery review to find out if it lives up to the hype.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/nextgen-gallery/\">NextGEN Gallery Review: Is It the Best Gallery Plugin?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15609:\"<p>Looking for the best image gallery plugin for WordPress? <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">NextGEN Gallery</a> is one of the oldest and most popular image gallery plugins in the WordPress.org directory, but is it the best? Read our NextGEN Gallery review to find out if it lives up to the hype.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-880\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review.png\" alt=\"NextGEN Gallery review\" width=\"964\" height=\"307\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review.png 964w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-300x96.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-768x245.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 964px) 100vw, 964px\" /></p>\n<h3>About NextGEN Gallery</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">NextGEN Gallery</a> is a free and premium WordPress gallery plugin created by Imagely in 2007. Since its release, it’s been popular among WordPress users, making it the most widely-used WordPress gallery plugin to date. The free version of the plugin has over 1 million active installs worldwide. </p>\n<p>Although it has the highest number of downloads and installs, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">NextGEN Gallery</a> has received mixed user responses. The plugin&#8217;s average rating on the official WordPress.org plugins page is 3.2 out of 5 stars. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">NextGEN Gallery plugin</a> allows you to create beautiful photo galleries and albums in WordPress. Additionally, you can upload photos in bulk, import metadata, add/delete/rearrange photos, edit thumbnails, and group galleries into albums. It’s a complete gallery management tool for WordPress. </p>\n<p>Despite a few drawbacks reported on WordPress.org, which we&#8217;ll get into below, it’s still the most widely-used WordPress gallery plugin available based on its multiple features. </p>\n<h3>Do You Need an Image Gallery Plugin?</h3>\n<p>If your website is heavily image-focused, you’ve probably noticed WordPress’s shortcomings in that area. WordPress was built primarily for blogs with a focus on written content.</p>\n<p>If you’re a photographer, <a title=\"Thinking of Starting a WordPress Web Design Business – Here 7 Things You Must Do\" href=\"http://www.wpbeginner.com/opinion/thinking-of-starting-a-wordpress-web-design-business-here-7-things-you-must-do/\" target=\"_blank\">designer</a>, artist, or any other profession that relies on visual content, you’ll have a lot of images to share with your website visitors.</p>\n<p>Without question, the best way to organize and display those images is with image galleries.</p>\n<p>The only issue is finding an image gallery plugin that’s easy to use, makes your images look great, and won&#8217;t slow down your site.</p>\n<h3>NextGEN Gallery Features</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">NextGEN Gallery</a> has a number of ways to help you organize your images, including:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>batch uploading images</li>\n<li>importing metadata from your photos</li>\n<li>grouping galleries into albums</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once you’ve uploaded your images, you can group them together to create either a slideshow or a thumbnail gallery.</p>\n<p>For each gallery, you can control the size, style, timing, transitions, controls, lightbox effects, and more.</p>\n<p>There&#8217;re also plenty of premium add-on plugins available. Each add-on adds a new type of gallery, such as mosaic, grid, or list-style galleries. You can purchase either NextGEN Plus for 8 new types of gallery displays, or NextGEN Pro for the 8 galleries plus more add-on plugins and pro support.</p>\n<h3>How to Create Your First NextGEN Gallery</h3>\n<p>After installing and activating the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">NextGEN Gallery plugin</a>, you can choose to allow or skip usage data collection and reporting.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-881\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-skip.jpg\" alt=\"NextGEN Gallery review - skip data collection\" width=\"491\" height=\"360\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-skip.jpg 491w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-skip-300x220.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 491px) 100vw, 491px\" /></p>\n<p>You’ll then be taken to the welcome screen, where there’s a short video that shows you how to create a basic gallery with the default options.</p>\n<p>If you navigate to <b>Gallery » Gallery Settings</b>, you can customize your gallery options. You should do this before you set up your first gallery, because some of the new settings won’t apply retroactively to galleries you’ve already created.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-883\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-settings.png\" alt=\"NextGEN Gallery review - settings\" width=\"578\" height=\"635\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-settings.png 578w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-settings-273x300.png 273w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 578px) 100vw, 578px\" /></p>\n<p>The settings are organized by the type of gallery you want to create. You can change the number of columns, the number of images to display, maximum image dimensions, etc. If you mouseover the information icons, you’ll see a tooltip with more details on what each option does and how it works.</p>\n<p>When your settings are saved, you can create your first gallery. Simply create a new page or post, or edit an existing page or post you’d like to insert your gallery into.</p>\n<p>To add your gallery, you can click either of the green buttons (the one that says “Add Gallery,” or the green button in your editor toolbar) &#8212; they both open the same window.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-884\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-add-new-gallery.jpg\" alt=\"NextGEN Gallery review - click the green button. Either one.\" width=\"501\" height=\"251\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-add-new-gallery.jpg 501w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-add-new-gallery-300x150.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 501px) 100vw, 501px\" /></p>\n<p>Click the <b>Add Gallery / Images</b> tab at the top to upload or choose the images you’d like to include.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-887\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-add-images.png\" alt=\"NextGEN Gallery review - figure out how to add images\" width=\"861\" height=\"318\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-add-images.png 861w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-add-images-300x111.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-add-images-768x284.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 861px) 100vw, 861px\" /></p>\n<p>After uploading or choosing your images, a popup will appear. Don&#8217;t click the link!</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-886\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-popup.png\" alt=\"NextGEN Gallery review - don\'t click the link! it\'s a trap\" width=\"323\" height=\"114\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-popup.png 323w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-popup-300x106.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 323px) 100vw, 323px\" /></p>\n<p>If you click the “Manage Gallery” link, it will open in a whole new window. Instead, just click the “X.”</p>\n<p>Now, click on the <b>Display Galleries</b> tab to insert your gallery on the page.</p>\n<p>Don’t click the <b>Insert Displayed Galleries</b> button yet! It will insert an empty gallery. Instead, you have to click the <b>What would you like to display?</b> section to expand it.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-888\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-display.png\" alt=\"NextGEN Gallery review - select the gallery\" width=\"626\" height=\"405\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-display.png 626w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-display-300x194.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" /></p>\n<p>Then under “Sources,” select “Galleries.”</p>\n<p>Under “Galleries,” click the empty field to display a list of your galleries. The one you just created should show up. Be sure to select it.</p>\n<p><i>Now </i>you can click the <b>Insert Displayed Galleries</b> button, and the gallery you just created should appear. However, you won’t see it in the visual editor. Instead, you’ll see this thumbnail:</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-889\" src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/nextgen-gallery-review-thumb.png\" alt=\"NextGEN Gallery review - mystery thumbnail\" width=\"298\" height=\"198\" /></p>\n<p>You’ll have to save your draft and preview the page to make sure it’s working.</p>\n<h3>Documentation and Support</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">NextGEN Gallery</a> provides extensive documentation for each and every feature on their website, with walkthroughs of all the technical details, as well as help for troubleshooting and solving the most common issues. They also offer a selection of tutorial videos.</p>\n<p>The developers do offer active support in the WordPress.org support forums. However, some reviews complained about the quality of their support.</p>\n<h3>Pricing for NextGEN Gallery Plugin</h3>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">NextGEN Gallery</a> core plugin is available for free in the official WordPress plugin repository. You can download it free from there and use it on as many sites as you want. </p>\n<p>Yet, there’re dozens of powerful Pro extensions created to add power to the core plugin. The Pro extensions are used for enhancing the gallery displays, creating lightboxs, enabling eCommerce, and connecting social networks. </p>\n<p>If you want to use the plugin extensions, you must purchase one of their premium plans. They have basically 3 pricing plans of which 2 are specifically for the NextGen Gallery Pro extensions. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/nextgen-gallery-pro-pricing.jpg\" alt=\"nextgen-gallery-pro-pricing\" width=\"775\" height=\"496\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222936\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/nextgen-gallery-pro-pricing.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/nextgen-gallery-pro-pricing-300x192.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/nextgen-gallery-pro-pricing-768x492.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>The first plan is <strong>Next Plus</strong>, which costs $79. If you purchase this plan, you’ll get all the gallery extensions and pro lightbox extensions. </p>\n<p>The second plan is called <strong>NextGEN Pro</strong>, which costs $99. It includes all the extensions provided in the Plus plan with additional eCommerce extensions and a Lightroom plugin. Thus, if you want to use all of NextGEN Gallery Pro&#8217;s extensions, you&#8217;ll need to purchase the Pro plan. </p>\n<p>The other plan is the <strong>All Themes + Plugins</strong> plan, which provides you access to all the NextGEN Pro extensions as well as all the themes created by Imagely. </p>\n<p>All these three plans come with 1 year of premium support and updates. They also have a <strong>Lifetime Everything</strong> plan that lets you use all the Imagely themes and plugins with support and updates forever. </p>\n<h3>NextGEN Gallery vs. Envira Gallery</h3>\n<p>Want to make your images look great, without spending lots of time trying to figure out how to use a new plugin?</p>\n<p>Then you need the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\">best image gallery plugin</a> available: one that can create beautiful galleries, has lots of customization options while still being easy to use, and won&#8217;t slow down your site.</p>\n<p>Unfortunately, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">NextGEN Gallery</a> falls flat on most of these requirements. See our verdict below for why.</p>\n<p>Of the 2 plugins, only <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Envira Gallery</a> meets all of those expectations. It’s easy to use, intuitive, fast, and creates beautiful galleries. See our full <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/envira-gallery/\">Envira Gallery Review</a> for more details.</p>\n<p>If you’ve already started using NextGEN Gallery and want to switch to Envira, it’s easy &#8212; just see this guide on <a href=\"http://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/how-to-switch-from-nextgen-to-envira-gallery-in-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\">How to Switch From NextGEN to Envira Gallery in WordPress</a>.</p>\n<h3>Our Verdict on Using NextGen Gallery</h3>\n<p>If you’re looking for a quick and easy way to create beautiful galleries on your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress site</a>, we believe <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">NextGEN Gallery</a> isn&#8217;t a good choice.</p>\n<p>While NextGEN Gallery has been one of the most popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\">WordPress gallery plugins</a> for almost a decade, its reviews are not so good: it’s rated just 3.2 out of 5 stars on WordPress.org.</p>\n<p>The main issue is that NextGEN Gallery has a steep learning curve &#8212; the user interface is incredibly unintuitive.</p>\n<p>While it does have a huge array of customization options, they’re difficult to navigate to find the options you need. You can create nice galleries with NextGEN Gallery, but it&#8217;ll take you a long time to learn how to configure your settings and get your galleries the way you want them to look.</p>\n<p>We’ve also noticed that <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">NextGEN Gallery</a> seems to use a lot of resources and slows down the WordPress admin. See <a href=\"http://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/how-wordpress-plugins-affect-your-sites-load-time/\" target=\"_blank\">How WordPress Plugins Affect Your Site’s Load Time</a> for more details.</p>\n<p>We give <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">NextGEN Gallery</a> 4.1 out of 5 stars. Here&#8217;s the breakdown of our review scores:</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/nextgen-gallery/\">NextGEN Gallery Review: Is It the Best Gallery Plugin?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/nextgen-gallery/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"15 Best Content Marketing Tools and Plugins for WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-content-marketing-tools-plugins-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-content-marketing-tools-plugins-wordpress/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 02 Oct 2018 09:32:39 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"content marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"content strategy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"wordpress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=222959\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:625:\"<p>Are you looking for the best content marketing tools and plugins? Of course you are! You wouldn’t have clicked on this article if you weren’t. Having the right set of tools and plugins for your WordPress website can take your content marketing strategies to the next level, elevating you to new levels of success. In [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-content-marketing-tools-plugins-wordpress/\">15 Best Content Marketing Tools and Plugins for WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20609:\"<p>Are you looking for the best content marketing tools and plugins? Of course you are! You wouldn’t have clicked on this article if you weren’t.</p>\n<p>Having the right set of tools and plugins for your WordPress website can take your content marketing strategies to the next level, elevating you to new levels of success.</p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll share the 15 best content marketing tools and plugins for WordPress websites available.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\">1. MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsights.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights\" width=\"775\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-217048\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsights.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsights-300x97.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsights-768x248.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Tracking user engagement is a huge part of creating a successful content strategy. So is knowing your overall traffic metrics. Well, guess what: MonsterInsights helps you do both!</p>\n<p>By quickly and easily <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-google-analytics-wordpress-site/\">connecting your WordPress site with your Google Analytics account</a>, MonsterInsights lets you view traffic and engagement reports directly from your Admin dashboard.</p>\n<p>Discover how visitors find and use your website, and adjust your strategies accordingly.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Started with MonsterInsights Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">2. OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-wordpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"optinmonster-wordpress-plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221492\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-wordpress-plugin.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-wordpress-plugin-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-wordpress-plugin-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Do you have a high bounce rate? If visitors are landing on your website and leaving immediately, there’s a good chance they’ll never come back… Unless you use OptinMonster.</p>\n<p>With its patented Exit-Intent® Technology, OptinMonster catches users right before they click out of your website and shows them a message to convert them into subscribers, customers, or followers.</p>\n<p>As the best lead generation tool on the market, OptinMonster allows you to create gorgeous optin forms that you can effortlessly connect with your email marketing service or CRM software. Use this plugin to increase user engagement, lower your bounce rate, and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/tips-get-email-subscribers/\">skyrocket your email subscriptions</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Started with OptinMonster Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/grammarly/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Grammarly</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/grammarly/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/grammarly-content-marketing-tools.png\" alt=\"grammarly-best content marketing tools\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223019\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/grammarly-content-marketing-tools.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/grammarly-content-marketing-tools-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/grammarly-content-marketing-tools-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Without great content, there would be no content marketing. If your content isn’t up to snuff, and leaves your readers questioning your expertise due to grammatical errors, then Grammarly is the tool for you.</p>\n<p>Grammarly is the leading online grammar checking tool, and can be used just about anywhere, including your WordPress posts editor or your internet browser (they have add-ons for Google Chrome, Firefox, and Microsoft Edge).</p>\n<p>If you, or your content writing team, are ESL then this tool will help you sound more natural and professional to native English readers. Or, if you’re a native English speaker, but writing just isn’t your thing, Grammarly can help you hone your skills.</p>\n<p>Once installed, Grammarly will highlight all grammar, spelling, and contextual errors in your content.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/grammarly/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Grammarly Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.canva.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Canva</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.canva.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Canva.png\" alt=\"Canva\" width=\"775\" height=\"288\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222962\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Canva.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Canva-300x111.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Canva-768x285.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Writing is the main element of good content marketing; however, professional visuals can turn “good” into “great.” With beautiful images to go along with your content, your chances for success increase exponentially.</p>\n<p>Canva allows you to make your own graphics, icons, infographics, and banners without having to break the bank for expensive editing software.</p>\n<p>This simple-yet-powerful image editing tool runs in your browser, and comes with a vast number of templates to assist you. Once you’ve finished your edits, export the image you’ve created and use it on your WordPress website.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.canva.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Canva Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/resmushit-image-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. reSmush.it</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/resmushit-image-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/resumsh-it-best-content-marketing-tools.png\" alt=\"resumsh it-best content marketing tools\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223021\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/resumsh-it-best-content-marketing-tools.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/resumsh-it-best-content-marketing-tools-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/resumsh-it-best-content-marketing-tools-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Once you’ve created, bought, or found an image you want to use on your website, use the reSmush.it plugin to compress it.</p>\n<p>Why? Because large images take longer to load and will slow down your website’s speed and performance, negatively affecting your users’ experience.</p>\n<p>reSmush.it shrinks the size of your image files without affecting quality. You can also optimize image files in bulk, and even optimize older images you’ve already used on your site.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/resmushit-image-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with reSmush.it Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Yoast SEO</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yoast-seo.png\" alt=\"Yoast SEO\" width=\"775\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-217166\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yoast-seo.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yoast-seo-300x97.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yoast-seo-768x248.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>No one will view your content if they can’t find it. That’s why it’s important to pay attention to your SEO (search engine optimization) so you can get a higher search rank on Google.</p>\n<p>As the world’s best WordPress SEO plugin, Yoast SEO helps you harness the full power of search engine optimization to boost your content’s rankings. It’s a full-featured SEO suite, that goes far beyond meta descriptions and tags. You’ll be forced to choose a focus keyword so your entire post can be graded and optimized, not just your meta data.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Yoast SEO Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/semrush/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. SEMRush</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/semrush/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/semrush.png\" alt=\"semrush\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218516\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/semrush.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/semrush-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/semrush-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>SEMRush is the favorite SEO tool chosen by thousands of professionals. If you want an in-depth peek into your competitors’ top organic keywords, advertising strategies, backlink techniques, and so much more, then SEMRush is the tool you need.</p>\n<p>With insights into your competitors’ SEO strategies, you can more-easily improve your own content marketing to keep up the pace. SEMRush also shares keywords you can easily rank for, keeps track of your backlinks, and provides other useful reports and data to help you succeed.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/semrush/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with SEMRush Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/title-and-nofollow-for-links/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Title and Nofollow for Links</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/title-and-nofollow-for-links/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/insert-title-and-nofollow-for-links.png\" alt=\"insert-title-and-nofollow-for-links\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223020\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/insert-title-and-nofollow-for-links.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/insert-title-and-nofollow-for-links-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/insert-title-and-nofollow-for-links-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>By default, WordPress doesn’t come with an option to add nofollow tags. This is unfortunate because most SEO experts recommend using nofollow tags for external links.</p>\n<p>Luckily, the Title and Nofollow for Links plugin exists to fix this issue!</p>\n<p>With this handy plugin, you can easily add title and nofollow options via WordPress’ insert link popup in the posts and pages editor.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/title-and-nofollow-for-links/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Title and Nofollow for Links Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/edit-flow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Edit Flow</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/edit-flow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/edit-flow-best-content-marketing-tools.png\" alt=\"edit flow-best content marketing tools\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223024\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/edit-flow-best-content-marketing-tools.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/edit-flow-best-content-marketing-tools-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/edit-flow-best-content-marketing-tools-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Having a blog as a part of your content marketing strategy is useless if you don’t update it consistently. By using the Edit Flow plugin, you can set up your WordPress blog to add custom posts statuses, view an editorial calendar, and even leave editorial feedback for your writers.</p>\n<p>Edit Flow is a must-have plugin if you’re running a multi-author blog as part of your content marketing strategy.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/edit-flow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Edit Flow Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"http://asana.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. Asana</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://asana.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/asana-content-marketing-tools.png\" alt=\"asana content marketing tools\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223022\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/asana-content-marketing-tools.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/asana-content-marketing-tools-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/asana-content-marketing-tools-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Have an entire team to manage? If so, then Asana is the project management tool you’ve been craving.</p>\n<p>Rather than wasting time with multiple emails, Asana organizes your tasks and conversations in one area. Increase your efficiency by not having to switch between endless emails and actual productivity!</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://asana.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Asana Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ahrefs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">11. Ahrefs</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ahrefs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Ahrefs.jpg\" alt=\"Ahrefs\" width=\"775\" height=\"354\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222968\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Ahrefs.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Ahrefs-300x137.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Ahrefs-768x351.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Ahrefs uses powerful crawlers to monitor the web, and, by using their service, you can utilize those crawlers to scope out your competition. Quickly and easily discover why your competitors are ranking higher than you are, and how you can turn the tables on them!</p>\n<p>Track your backlinks and your competitors’ backlinks. Figure out the best paid advertising keywords. Or, use the content research tools to improve your blog posts.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ahrefs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Ahrefs Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://ifttt.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">12. IFTTT</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ifttt.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/IFTTT.png\" alt=\"IFTTT\" width=\"775\" height=\"287\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222967\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/IFTTT.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/IFTTT-300x111.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/IFTTT-768x284.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Automate your social media accounts with IFTTT. You can easily connect with all the popular social networking sites, as well as WordPress and other services.</p>\n<p>Trigger retweets, share images, automatically share your WordPress blog posts on social media, and so much more.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ifttt.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with IFTTT Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/shared-counts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">13. Shared Counts</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/shared-counts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sharedcounts.jpg\" alt=\"Shared Counts\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222090\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sharedcounts.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sharedcounts-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sharedcounts-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>GDPR compliant and easy-to-use, Shared Counts is among the very best social media plugins for WordPress. It lets you add social media sharing buttons to your blog posts with ease.</p>\n<p>You can also display share counts, and the total number of shares for each article. And, unlike other plugins of this nature, Shared Counts won’t slow down your website!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/shared-counts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Shared Counts Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"http://buzzsumo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">14. BuzzSumo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://buzzsumo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/buzzsumo.png\" alt=\"buzzsumo\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218518\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/buzzsumo.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/buzzsumo-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/buzzsumo-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Enter in a keyword and find out what type of content performs best for it. Sound easy? It is. That’s why we love BuzzSumo.</p>\n<p>This unique tool also lets you discover key influencers in your niche, and helps you figure out the best strategy to email them, send a pitch, and get them to promote your content.</p>\n<p>Need help with an eye-catching, high-performing headline? BuzzSumo will analyze your topic choice, and report back with the most popular headlines, organized by social share rankings.</p>\n<p>You can even set alerts for your favorite keywords to stay on top of up-and-coming trends!</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://buzzsumo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with BuzzSumo Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">15. Revive Old Posts</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost.jpg\" alt=\"Revive Old Posts\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222749\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If your older articles are still relevant, why not continue to share them? With the Revive Old Posts plugin, you can automatically share older blog posts on your social media accounts. Just set it, forget it, and let it do the work for you.</p>\n<p>By promoting old articles, you maintain a consistent online presence on social media; and new followers get to catch up on posts they may have missed out on previously.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Revive Old Posts Today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best content marketing tools and plugins for WordPress.</p>\n<p>If you enjoyed this list, you might also love reading our list of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-business-themes/\">25 best business themes for your WordPress website</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-content-marketing-tools-plugins-wordpress/\">15 Best Content Marketing Tools and Plugins for WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\